{"id":345715,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/05/多维新闻-中国10天内3位报业大佬自杀/","date":"2014-05-09T04:29:16Z","modified":"2014-05-09T07:34:29Z","title":"多维新闻 | 中国10天内3位报业大佬自杀","content":"<p>据大陆媒体“记者站网”5月8日下午19时报道，深圳报业集团晶报原编委、广告部总经理张敬武自杀！据知情人士透露，张敬武7日晚失踪，8日在深圳香蜜湖一处涵洞发现尸体，留有遗书。分析人士表示，从4月28日新华社安徽分社副社长、总编辑宋斌自杀，5月4日杭州《都市快报》35岁的副总编徐行自杀到张敬武，短短的10天之内，中国大陆3位知名媒体人相继自杀实属罕见，而官方给出的罹患抑郁症的自杀理由似乎也过于草率。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-345715 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/05/%e5%a4%9a%e7%bb%b4%e6%96%b0%e9%97%bb-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd10%e5%a4%a9%e5%86%853%e4%bd%8d%e6%8a%a5%e4%b8%9a%e5%a4%a7%e4%bd%ac%e8%87%aa%e6%9d%80/ab4df43f12640fa2503cb5af7ad2bdb1/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/05/ab4df43f12640fa2503cb5af7ad2bdb1-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-345716\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/05/ab4df43f12640fa2503cb5af7ad2bdb1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/05/ab4df43f12640fa2503cb5af7ad2bdb1-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-345716'>\n\t\t\t\t张敬武微博截图\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/